{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"996a0a89b6","title":"对刘少奇、杨尚昆破坏纪律擅自以中央名义发出文件的批评","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1975207f0c","index":0,"year":1953,"month":5,"day":19,"articleId":"996a0a89b6"}],"tags":[{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoxuan-jinghuo","name":"毛泽东选集1-7（静火版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"静火","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/maoxuan-jinghuo.pdf"},{"id":"xuanji5","name":"毛泽东选集第五卷（1977）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"毛泽东","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/毛泽东选集(1977)5.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoxuan-jinghuo":{"comments":[{"id":"6b4890597c","publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"996a0a89b6","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"这是毛泽东同志对刘少奇、杨尚昆的两次书面批评。"}],"contents":[{"id":"e63c07c050","type":"title","text":"对刘少奇、杨尚昆破坏纪律擅自以中央名义发出文件的批评","index":0,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"996a0a89b6"},{"id":"5d4995eeb4","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"996a0a89b6"},{"id":"5a7a15e206","type":"paragraph","text":"嗣后，凡用中央名义发出的文件、电报，均须经我看过方能发出，否则无效。请注意。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"996a0a89b6"},{"id":"c91448715e","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":3,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"996a0a89b6"},{"id":"7900b898cc","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）请负责检查自去年八月一日（八一以前的有过检查）至今年五月五日用中央和军委名义发出的电报和文件，是否有及有多少未经我看过的（我出巡及患病请假时间内者不算在内），以其结果告我；","index":4,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"996a0a89b6"},{"id":"7b301d4daa","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）过去数次中央会议决议不经我看，擅自发出，是错误的，是破坏纪律的。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"996a